query:
SELECT
                number,
                pubdata_input
            FROM
                l1_batches
                LEFT JOIN data_availability ON data_availability.l1_batch_number = l1_batches.number
            WHERE
                is_sealed
                AND eth_commit_tx_id IS NULL
                AND number != 0
                AND data_availability.blob_id IS NULL
                AND pubdata_input IS NOT NULL
            ORDER BY
                number
            LIMIT
                $1
